data.description: This is a property you will not want to miss! Meticulously maintained, professionally landscaped, and completely updated so it is ready for you to move in and enjoy. The large open concept kitchen/dining area has black stainless appliances and lots of cabinet, counter and seating space. The main floor also has a formal dining room and half bath with much of the flooring throughout being hardwood floors. The sellers added an addition to the back of the house that is now a large primary suite on the main floor that has a walk-in closet, bathroom and laundry. The open staircase in the living room leads to the 2nd floor where there are 2 more bedrooms, a large storage closet or office space and a full bath with a double sink. You won't have to worry about internet speed here with fiber optic. This is one of the bigger lots in town with a .38 lot size. The back yard is quite an experience to enjoy with a concrete and paver patio area, screened patio area, pool, screened chain link privacy fenced yard, and garden shed. The 2-1/2 car garage was just built in 2015.
